metadata.name: DOOMCOLLAGE_ACP
metadata.description:
Mixed Media work of MF DOOM.

The illest villain. Remember all caps when you spell the man's name.

A precursor to @acommonplacenft. Coming soon. 

Spraypaint and marker on canvas.

*If the auction winner wishes to have the physical piece they can, but shipping is at the cost of the purchaser.*
